title: Dark Star Corruption Icon
body:
Saw someone else who had the same issue on the board, so I figured I'd ask for some help as well.
I'm pretty confident that I won at least one game of the Dark Star game mode with two other friends when it was available. But it's June and I still haven't received the icon. Could I have some assistance please?

replies.body: Sometimes the delivery poros run a little late. Make sure to double check for the Corruption Icon now!

> [{quoted}](name=Broporo,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=EmKuP3zT,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2017-06-05T00:43:20.657+0000)
>
> Sometimes the delivery poros run a little late. Make sure to double check for the Corruption Icon now!

Sorry I'm late to check back on the post. Thank you very much for your help!
My very first game was won with 2 friends and I still haven't received mine either.    :(
